<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <%- include('./partials/head') %>
  <script type="text/javascript" defer>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      const elems = document.querySelectorAll('.modal');
      const instances = M.Modal.init(elems);
    });
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      var elem = document.querySelectorAll('.parallax');
      var instances = M.Parallax.init(elem);
    });
  </script>
  <script src="js/authEventHandlers.js" type="text/javascript" defer></script>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>
  </header>
  <main>
    <div class="parallax-container">
      <div class="parallax"><img src="/img/start-background1.jpg"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section white">
      <div class="container">
        <h4 class='start-h5 center'>Find Your Favorite Recipe and Organize Potlucks</h4>
        <div class="row start-page">
          <div class="grid-example col s12 m6 l6">
            <div class='col-content start-info'>
              <span>Getting tired of same old dishes? <br>You're in the right place. <br> Search from 1.7+ million nutritionally analyzed recipes.
                Detailed macro and micronutrient data
                Filter by calories, diets and allergens.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid-example col s12 m6 l6 ">
            <div class='col-content start-info'>
              <span>Looking for potluck ideas? <br> Impress friends and family with these crowd-pleasing potluck recipes that range from appetizers and beverages to dinners, salads, sandwiches, side dishes, soups and chilis, desserts and more.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


      <div class='start-register center'>
        <a href="#modal1" class="waves-effect waves-light btn #b71c1c red darken-4 modal-trigger">Get Started</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="parallax-container">
      <div class="parallax"><img src="/img/start-background.jpg"></div>
    </div>
    <div id="modal1" class="modal start">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <h5>Registration</h5>
        <form action="/auth/register" method="post">
          Username: <input id='register-username' type="text" name="username">
          Password: <input id='register-password' type="password" name="password">
          Confirm Password: <input id='register-password-confirm' type="password" name="passwordConfirm">
          <p class="register-message message"></p>
          <button type="submit" id="register-btn" class="btn waves-effect waves-light">Submit</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="modal2" class="modal start">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <h5>Login</h5>
        <p class='center'>Welcome back.</p>
        <form action="/auth/login" method="post">
          Username: <input id='login-username' type="text" name="username">
          Password: <input id='login-password' type="password" name="password">
          <p class="login-message message"></p>
          <button type="submit" id="login-btn" class="btn waves-effect waves-light">Submit</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include('./partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>
